unittitle_ssm: Brooklyn Treasurer and City Court Clerk receipt books
abstract_ssm: This collection contains a receipt book of the Village of Brooklyn with entries for payments by John S. Doughty Jr., the Village Treasurer, dated 1827. Also included is a receipt book of the City Court Clerk of the City of Brooklyn with entries for payments to court officers, dated 1869
